Using @Embeddable, @EmbeddedId annotations for this.

@Embeddable: to place on the top of ID class indicating that this is not a entity class it is Embaddable 
id class to entity class.

@EmbeddedId: to configure special id proerty as the composite id.
NOTE:: Generater configuration to generate the ID value is posssible only while working with singular Id field, not while working with composite id field.
